tatami.core.agent.visualization

Class Log2AgentGui

  • java.lang.Object
    • tatami.core.agent.visualization.Log2AgentGui
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    net.xqhs.util.logging.DisplayEntity

    public class Log2AgentGui
extends java.lang.Object
implements net.xqhs.util.logging.DisplayEntity
    The class makes the link between a log (needing a DisplayEntity instance) and the appropriate component in an agent GUI.

    Whenever the log posts something, by calling the output() method, the logging message is relayed to the GUI component by means of the doOutput() method in AgentGui.

    Author:
    Andrei Olaru
